This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with generating photo-realistic images from text descriptions. It also involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel model that involves learning and disentangling semantics, which could fall under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the experiments are conducted on image datasets, which could also suggest that it belongs to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
